{"tid":2183203,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"我真係好愛你，可唔可以重頭黎過","createTime":"2020-08-31T20:12:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-01T04:12:09.000Z","uid":23267,"like":8,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"6ff2119b86b7f6478cd5b597bac9e85e81bce796","tid":2183203,"uid":23267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T20:12:44.000Z","msg":"咁就四個月，分咗手四個月。過咗四個月我以為自己已經開始放低，原來無，我放唔低。我好掛住你，發夢都夢見你返黎搵我，呢幾個月夢過你幾多次我都數唔到，我真係好掛住你。<br />\n<br />\n原來呢個世界真係會有一個人同自己咁夾，當時每日都過得好開心，每日都見，大家都習慣咗身邊有對方，我都終於可以係另一半面前做返自己。你當初話玩夠啦想停低，點解到最後一個原因都唔比我就離開我。<br />\n<br />\n點解明知自己性格係咁，要比咁多承諾我。我好想繼續留係你身邊，我真係好愛你，我地可唔可以重頭黎過。"},{"pid":"0d14dbd41d3be8b277fc2153580d9785d759e97f","tid":2183203,"uid":9392,"like":16,"dislike":2,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T20:16:47.000Z","msg":"你慳啲屌你老母"},{"pid":"e61c4e04e986f1bfa8817633b01e15a13c4fd2e0","tid":2183203,"uid":9392,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T20:17:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你慳啲啦屌你老母</blockquote>"},{"pid":"93efbdb4ea3eb2d11cacbd22bf44143ebf43133b","tid":2183203,"uid":21255,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T20:18:35.000Z","msg":"sor 牙<br />\n唔啦😂😅😅"},{"pid":"185c8bf0778d4a8b503367bfe0db7bc7acc2ea13","tid":2183203,"uid":261914,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T20:20:36.000Z","msg":"原諒我係一隻無腳嘅雀仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce8c96cea017023dbb96172d81fd8af70b0ad982","tid":2183203,"uid":15605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T20:34:54.000Z","msg":"已經屌厭，唔可以"},{"pid":"bd3f1d7b9294c50fd28000c2c1ffc6fab049a859","tid":2183203,"uid":193004,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T21:00:09.000Z","msg":"人哋屌緊第條女啦得撚閒諗你咩傻閪醒吓啦"},{"pid":"47daf2d012bba92545dbb1f37749cbe37bc00723","tid":2183203,"uid":99700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T21:02:10.000Z","msg":"好呀 下世啦"},{"pid":"e4c74fbdca1b8578bb29f4